Class InputOutput

java.lang.Object
com.gameplay.InputOutput
public class InputOutput extends Object
InputOutput class manages all Input and Output operations that are used in Map Editor and Gameplay.

  • Method Details

    • get_user_command

      public static Parsing get_user_command()
      Prompts user to enter a command, perform command validation, and returns Command object where the user command has been parsed.

      The method accepts the following user commands:

      • editcontinent
      • editcountry
      • editneighbor
      • showmap
      • savemap
      • editmap
      • validatemap
      • loadmap
      • gameplayer
      • assigncountries
      • deploy
      Returns:
      A new Parsing object where the user command has been parsed, otherwise null if the provided user command does not match any commands
